              </p>

              <p style="
                    font-size: 36px;
                    letter-spacing: 10px;
                    font-weight: bold;
                    text-align: center;
                    margin: 30px 0;
                  ">
                <%= otp %>
              </p>

              <p>
                This code is valid for the next 10 minutes. Please do not
